<div class="main-content">
  <div class="content-header">
    <h2>Hello World</h2>
    <div class="timestamp">Generated at: <%= timestamp %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content-body">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        Greeting
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3 style="color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><%= message %></h3>
        <p>This is a simple hello world page demonstrating the SDB Analyzer web interface.</p>
        <p>You have successfully accessed this authenticated web application!</p>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        How This Works
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>This web interface is built using:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
          <li><strong>Rack</strong> - The foundation web server interface</li>
          <li><strong>ERB Templates</strong> - For rendering HTML views</li>
          <li><strong>HTTP Basic Authentication</strong> - Secure access protection</li>
          <li><strong>Session Management</strong> - Cookie-based sessions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">This follows the same pattern as <a href="https://github.com/sidekiq/sidekiq" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">Sidekiq's web interface</a>, providing a clean, secure, and maintainable web UI without heavy framework dependencies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 